@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000
@tenantId = 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001
@accessToken = {{token}}

### Get Departments (Paged)
GET {{baseUrl}}/departments?pageIndex=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### Get Departments (All)
GET {{baseUrl}}/departments/all
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### Create Department
POST {{baseUrl}}/departments
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

{
  "name": "Head Office",
  "parentId": null,
  "sortOrder": 0
}

### Update Department
PUT {{baseUrl}}/departments/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

{
  "name": "Head Office",
  "parentId": null,
  "sortOrder": 0
}